CONTRIBUTING

We love pull requests from everyone. Please be polite and courteous in messages
and comments with other contributers.

Fork the repo first, then clone your repo:

    git clone git@github.com:YOURUSERNAME/heimdall.git

You should probably setup a virtualenv, and pip install from requirements.txt.

Push to your fork and submit a pull request:

	https://github.com/DistilledLtd/heimdall/compare/

At this point you're waiting on us. We will try to be as quick as possible with
commenting on and accepting pull requests.

Some things that will increase the chance that your pull request is accepted:

	- Please stick to PEP8
	- Only PEP8 exception: we allow lines to run to 99 characters.
	- Comments should still be 72 characters or less.
	- Write a useful and clear commit message.
